s332: Establishes Yang Mausoleum town. Chancellor Bei Ping Hou Zhang Cang passes away.
s338: Moves Guangchuan King Peng Zu to Zhao King.
s341: Imperial Secretary Yang Ling Hou Cen Mai.
s344: Deposes Crown Prince Rong as Linjiang King. Fourth month ding si, Jiaodong King established as Crown Prince. Qing dismissed from chancellor.
s345: Sixth month yi si, Grand Commandant Marquis of Tiao Zhou Yafu becomes Chancellor. Abolishes Grand Commandant office.
s356: Imperial son Yue becomes Guangchuan King, Ji becomes Jiaodong King.
s362: Imperial son Cheng becomes Qinghe King. Yafu dismissed from chancellor.
s363: Four. Imperial Secretary Tao Hou Liu She becomes Chancellor.
s368: Linjiang King summoned, commits suicide, buried at Lan Tian, Yan several tens of thousands make clay figures placed on tomb.
s374: Imperial son Shun becomes Changshan King.
s380: Liang Xiao King Wu passes away. Divides Liang into five states, kings various sons: son Mai becomes Liang King, Ming becomes Ji Chuan King, Peng Li becomes Ji Dong King, Ding becomes Shan Yang King, Bu Shi becomes Ji Yin King.
s386: Fifth month, earth movement. Seventh month yi si, solar eclipse. She dismissed from chancellor.
s387: Five. Eighth month ren chen, Imperial Secretary Jian Ling Hou Wei Wan becomes Chancellor.
